OL,3,CHow the rise in AI romance scams is
OL,4,Ccosting lovers thousands
OL,6,F1) Watch for "love bombing." Scammers
OL,7,Foverwhelm victims with affection early
OL,8,Fon to gain trust.
OL,10,F2) Verify their identity. Use reverse
OL,11,Fimage searches and insist on live
OL,12,Fvideo calls which AI-generated
OL,13,Fscammers avoid.
OL,15,F3) Never send money. No real partner
OL,16,Fwill pressure you for financial
OL,17,Fhelp`especially when you've never met.
OL,19,F4) Be wary of celebrity DMs. If a
OL,20,Ffamous figure suddenly messages you,
OL,21,Fit's likely a scam.
